headline.print_headline: Borussia Dortmund's Reus Injured on Comeback
headline.main: Borussia Dortmund's Reus Injured on Comeback

lead_paragraph: Borussia Dortmund winger Marco Reus was taken off injured midway through the second half of their Bundesliga game against Paderborn after earlier scoring on his comeback from an ankle injury.
